# Pet Circle -- Screen Completion Guide

## Phase 1 Status: COMPLETE

All Phase 1 user stories are implemented including the care circle role system (Admin/Member/Viewer).

## Role System

- Two app-level roles: Owner and Vet (selected at sign-in via role_selection_screen)
- Three care circle roles per pet: Admin, Member, Viewer (defined in `care_circle_member.dart`)
- `CareCirclePermissions` extension provides `canMeasure`, `canEditPet`, `canManageCircle`, `canAddNotes`, `canDeletePet`
- `PetStore.currentUserRoleFor(petName)` returns the current user's role for a given pet
- Pet detail edit button: admin-only
- Dashboard delete (long-press): admin-only
- Invite flow: offers Member or Viewer (Admin is auto-assigned to pet creator)

## Navigation Structure

```
Bottom Nav: Home(0) | Trends(1) | Measure(2) | Medication(3)
Trends tabs: Overview | Measurement History
Notifications: bell icon drawer only (no dedicated tab)
Medication: standalone screen at lib/screens/medication/medication_screen.dart
```

